He played college football at Fort Hays State. Williams was signed by the Green Bay Packers as an undrafted free agent in 2015. ==Professional career== After going undrafted in the 2015 NFL Draft, Williams signed with the Green Bay Packers on August 3, 2015. On September 5, 2015, he was released by the Packers during final team cuts. Williams was signed to the Packers' practice squad on September 8, 2015. On January 18, 2016, he was re-signed by the Packers after finishing the season on the practice squad.
